Enum DependencyRelationType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DependencyRelationType>
      • eu.excitement.entailment.core.representation.parsetree.DependencyRelationType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DependencyRelationType>

    public enum DependencyRelationType
extends java.lang.Enum<DependencyRelationType>
    Dependency Relation Types, according to the adopted UIMA dependency type. (DKPro.type.dependency.Dependency subtypes) Updating this enum must be done according to this UIMA type.

    Gil
